desc: Aktivbar is a protein bar made with simple, clean ingredients powered by functional mushrooms well known for their health and performance benefits. With under 200 calories in a bar, no added sugar, and real, authentic taste, you get the energy and immunity boost necessary for an active and healthy life.

layout.text: PROTEIN AND ENERGY BARS POWERED BY FUNCTIONAL MUSHROOMS
Clean. Simple. Delicious. Life Nutrients Packed In A Bar.
